title: Mamata seeks cooperation of anti-BJP parties to oust saffron party from Centre - The Indian Express
content: Mamata seeks cooperation of anti-BJP parties to oust saffron party from Centre  The Indian ExpressView Full coverage on Google News
description: The West Bengal Chief Minister said, “I feel sad to see that the Congress is fighting the election in favour of the BJP in Meghalaya and Chandigarh.”
